      <title>马来西亚考虑恢复消费税以刺激财政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/malaysia-weighs-bringing-back-consumption-tax-to-boost-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，马来西亚政府正考虑恢复广泛的消费税，而不是削减常用汽油的补贴，以增强财政实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/malaysia-weighs-bringing-back-consumption-tax-to-boost-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:51:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其计划增加伊斯坦布尔出租车数量以解决乘客投诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/turkey-to-increase-istanbul-taxi-numbers-over-complaints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，土耳其商业首都伊斯坦布尔的出租车难问题一直饱受诟病，土耳其计划增加该市的出租车数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/turkey-to-increase-istanbul-taxi-numbers-over-complaints</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:50:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗集团预计美联储 9 月份将降息 50 个基点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-28/citi-s-baldwin-sees-50-basis-point-fed-cut-in-september-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团全球研究主管露西·鲍德温 (Lucy Baldwin) 讨论了美联储利率、美国经济数据和股市前景。鲍德温周三在彭博电视台表示：“我们可能会在 9 月份大幅降息 50 个基点。我们预计从现在到年底，降息幅度将达到 125 个基点。” （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-28/citi-s-baldwin-sees-50-basis-point-fed-cut-in-september-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:46:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚石油产量因停产而每天减少 40 万桶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/libya-oil-output-drops-by-400-000-barrels-a-day-amid-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于在利比亚央行控制权争夺中出现僵局，油田减少作业，本周利比亚的石油产量几乎减少了一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/libya-oil-output-drops-by-400-000-barrels-a-day-amid-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:43:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于期限需求减弱，奥地利放弃出售 2086 年债券的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/austria-drops-plan-to-sell-long-bonds-as-duration-demand-wanes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利周三决定不再进行长期债券的银团发售，这是投资者对债券期限兴趣减弱的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/austria-drops-plan-to-sell-long-bonds-as-duration-demand-wanes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中海油报告上半年利润因石油钻探业务增长而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/cnooc-reports-higher-first-half-profits-on-oil-drilling-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的海上石油和天然气生产商中海油有限公司表示，由于产量增加和原油价格上涨，上半年利润有所增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/cnooc-reports-higher-first-half-profits-on-oil-drilling-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:34:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SAS 凭借新资本和新主席摆脱第 11 章破产保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/sas-picks-former-novo-executive-kare-schultz-to-lead-airline-after-chapter-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过两年的破产程序后，斯堪的纳维亚半岛的旗舰航空公司 SAS AB 目前归法航荷航集团和私募股权公司 Castlelake LP 所有，前诺和诺德公司高管 Kare Schultz 担任其新董事会主席。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/sas-picks-former-novo-executive-kare-schultz-to-lead-airline-after-chapter-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 05:56:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金增持股份，日本麒麟扩大对 Fancl 的收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/japan-s-kirin-again-extends-tender-offer-deadline-for-fancl</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麒麟控股株式会社将收购 Fancl 股份有限公司多数股权的最后期限延长了两周，因为一家对冲基金对目标公司进行悄悄收购引发了人们对其是否有能力控制这家日本护肤品和保健品制造商的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/japan-s-kirin-again-extends-tender-offer-deadline-for-fancl</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 05:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
